---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Navigation from '../components/Navigation.astro';

---

<Layout title="History">
  <Navigation />
  <main class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-primary mb-8">History of St. John Parade</h1>
    <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
      <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-secondary mb-4">Our Rich Heritage</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">
          The St. John Parade has been a cornerstone of our community's celebrations for generations, 
          bringing together people from all walks of life to celebrate our shared heritage and values.
        </p>
        
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-secondary mb-3">The Early Years</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">
          What started as a small community gathering has grown into one of the region's most 
          anticipated annual events, drawing participants and spectators from across the state.
        </p>

        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-secondary mb-3">Growing Tradition</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">
          Through the decades, the parade has evolved while maintaining its core mission of 
          celebrating community spirit and fostering local pride.
        </p>

        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-secondary mb-3">Modern Era</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700">
          Today, the St. John Parade continues to be a highlight of the community calendar, 
          featuring both traditional elements and modern additions that reflect our growing 
          and diverse community.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>